Text: TvTeam,rnrnThank you so much for posting the episodes of SYTYCD. I do not have a television, so you are making it possible for me to see my favorite show. I appreciate all of the work you do to post these episodes, and episodes from other great shows.rnrnIf you have SYTYCD S07 E08 and E13, I would love to watch them, if only to see the amazing group dance at the beginning of the results show.rnrnYou rock!
